ping : to check software or server is running or not connection is working fine or not
netstat : to check active internet connection.
tcp , local addres, state, bus sockets
ifconfig : network interface 
traceroute : route of website ip hopping from source to destination path
mtr : png + traceroute my trace route
nslookup : which ip address active on particular website
telnet : help to connect port of website connect http : 80 https :443
hostname : show the ip address of server





